OL,7,FThe mother of a 10-year-old girl who
OL,8,Fhas a rare genetic condition meaning
OL,9,Fshe can have up to 12 severe seizures
OL,10,Fa day is fundraising for a specialist
OL,11,Fseat to help keep her safe.
OL,13,FVivian Price, from Mumbles in Swansea,
OL,14,Fhas a condition called microcephaly,
OL,15,Fwhich is a neurological condition that
OL,16,Faffects all aspects of her life and
OL,17,Fmeans she has severe disabilities.
OL,19,FShe also experiences epileptic
OL,20,Fseizures, meaning she needs a
OL,21,Fspecialist chair to keep her safe.
