OL,7,FHer mother Helene told ITV Cymru
OL,8,FWales: "She just wants to be into
OL,9,Feverything and everyone she meets,
OL,10,Freally.
OL,12,F"She wakes up and before she opens her
OL,13,Feyes every morning she smiles and last
OL,14,Ftime just before she goes to bed she
OL,15,Fsmiles - she's a smiler and everyone
OL,16,Fjust loves her."
OL,18,FHelene says her daughter has a small
OL,19,Fbrain because her brain stopped
OL,20,Fdeveloping before she was born.
