OL,7,F"She is not mobile. She can walk but
OL,8,Fshe's very, very unsteady when she
OL,9,Fwalks so she's in a wheelchair.
OL,11,F"She has vision problems.
OL,13,F"She has no awareness of danger at all
OL,14,Fso she has to be watched all the time,
OL,15,Fshe loves to grab anything that's in
OL,16,Fher reach so we have to make sure
OL,17,Fshe's quite isolated and safe and
OL,18,Fsecure."
