OL,7,FAs for her daughter's seizures, Helene
OL,8,Fsaid: "They can last over an hour
OL,9,Fsometimes. We have periods where it
OL,10,Fgets better, periods where it gets
OL,11,Fworse."
OL,13,FVivian has outgrown her current chair
OL,14,Fand her family is now fundraising for
OL,15,Fa replacement, something they say
OL,16,Fwould make a huge difference.
